  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Saute the onion and garlic in olive oil until softened.",
    "Add the smoked paprika and caraway seeds and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lentils, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
